### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Obtener portfolio de un usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/1

### Buscar instrumentos
GET {{baseUrl}}/instruments/search?query=MACRO

### Crear una orden de mercado (MARKET)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instrumentId": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "side": "BUY",
  "size": 10,
  "type": "MARKET"
}

